{"tid":287451,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(太陽由西面升起？)tvb神級旅遊節目推介","createTime":"2017-06-17T12:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T15:19:09.000Z","uid":22242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"17bc8855f7d57a8e75abd0c2c499be751fdd0f46","tid":287451,"uid":22242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T12:10:28.000Z","msg":"本身以為cctvb既節目已經好垃圾 完全睇唔入眼<br />\n點知岩岩屋企食飯果陣唔小心睇tvb睇套到叫「超級台灣行」既旅遊節目 7點半星期六做既<br />\n呢套野真係可以用超級去形容 係超級垃圾<br />\n點解咁耐都可以無人屌 我今次真係忍唔撚到要開post講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1）男女主持本身已經唔掂<br />\n男既叫阿mark 圖就真係唔俾啦 因為真係肥 矮 柒集一身 口才完全唔好仲要串柒柒咁 見佢前而憎佢後面個款<br />\n女呢好普通樣 隨便係mk捉一個都一樣樣 又係口才一般<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2）每集都有個藝人俾個任務佢地做 之前我無睇 今次係叻哥俾任務已經唔洗講 仲要做埋啲傻的嗎任務 根本係浪費時間又無推廣任何旅遊地方<br />\n<br />\n3）成套野基本上除左講左個地點名同地址 根本係介紹過個景點/餐廳既特色 佢地所謂既介紹根本阿豬阿狗都講得出 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我以為tvb無任何競爭既情況下 近呢幾年已經垃圾到頂點 但睇完呢套野我發覺 原來沒有最垃圾 只有更垃圾 好期待下套更垃圾既節目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後附上女主持圖一張<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/201025_947ea6bebf0be277f3ce336cd8203444.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F201025_947ea6bebf0be277f3ce336cd8203444.jpg&h=474a5678&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74f8839077273c44e225d9c694668c1381576d1c","tid":287451,"uid":5883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T12:31:13.000Z","msg":"我睇向世界出發仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45bf8a8fb125163364f973788eb3366898191bb","tid":287451,"uid":22242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:45:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我睇向世界出發仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1171211b8a08a12ec95f51f8c29446879d0709a6","tid":287451,"uid":22242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1339b088a4c1ed3e8ef3a9b394da007a2b5451ff","tid":287451,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:47:22.000Z","msg":"唔小心睇tvb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8352ddbeaedc90c9d56c051992cf5dabfbddcb00","tid":287451,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:48:23.000Z","msg":"真 啱啱行過廳睇咗陣<br />\n真係好撚垃圾<br />\n打籃球個度唔知jm9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個男主持一大陣鳩屎味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反而女主持之前拍講美國既旅遊節目幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5330d2f27a88e215624cd4a2df16d9175f50fafc","tid":287451,"uid":61317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:51:11.000Z","msg":"個死肥佬好似係至矮個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2761b0f2bff0e626d6c340dd55e68507973ebd9d","tid":287451,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T15:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個死肥佬好似係至矮個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8735887f4278ff1b4dbe4d214bc20f0744c06e5d","tid":287451,"uid":60052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T15:15:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個死肥佬好似係至矮個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢講真。 真係志偉個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa